WEBVTT

00:00.164 --> 00:02.266
Welcome to Hilltop.

00:02.299 --> 00:03.945
No! No! Pete can't stay!

00:04.006 --> 00:06.365
Through Teachers-in-Service Day!

00:06.390 --> 00:07.772
You know, I don't know who Pete is,

00:07.805 --> 00:10.058
but I do know
that you're embarrassing him.

00:10.121 --> 00:12.024
Douglas, our beloved Hilltop parrot

00:12.057 --> 00:15.027
has to stay alone at school
over the three-day weekend.

00:15.059 --> 00:17.262
It's cruel. Inhumane.

00:17.295 --> 00:19.285
- Will you sign a petition...
- No.

00:20.836 --> 00:23.101
Did you just dismiss my
8-year-old daughter's activism?

00:23.134 --> 00:24.969
Activism? Come on.

00:25.003 --> 00:26.138
Don't be Lollypop Boy.

00:26.170 --> 00:27.538
What does that eve... I'm sorry.

00:27.571 --> 00:28.940
Am I supposed to
understand that reference?

00:28.974 --> 00:31.243
No. Honestly, it just got away from me.

00:31.276 --> 00:33.145
- Ah.
- Don't you ignore me, Rocco!

00:33.177 --> 00:34.836
Don't be a part of the problem!

00:34.883 --> 00:36.484
Pete shouldn't have to
spend the weekend alone,

00:36.517 --> 00:38.687
so Sophie's petitioning
Vice Principal Yarble

00:38.721 --> 00:40.022
to let us take him home with us.

00:40.055 --> 00:42.024
Man, I am so proud
of that kid's conscience.

00:42.056 --> 00:44.059
Oh, please. You do it
because it makes you look good.

00:44.092 --> 00:45.193
- What?
- The accolades.

00:45.227 --> 00:47.062
10 bucks says that
you're wearing a T-shirt

00:47.096 --> 00:48.497
- with Sophie's face on it.
- Pfft.

00:48.529 --> 00:50.166
- Unzip the sweater. Let me help you.
- I'm not going to.

00:50.199 --> 00:52.034
- Don't touch me! It's my body!
- Okay.

00:52.066 --> 00:53.535
All right, fine, but you know damn well

00:53.568 --> 00:55.471
my resolution was
to do more silk-screening.

00:55.504 --> 00:57.373
There you go.

00:57.406 --> 01:00.042
This is about helping Sophie
develop a strong moral compass.

01:00.074 --> 01:02.178
And, yes, I've picked out my suit

01:02.211 --> 01:03.646
for the Student of the Year ceremony.

01:03.679 --> 01:05.647
Heads-up, this guy's going with maroon.

01:05.681 --> 01:07.182
It's not a suit if it isn't black.

01:07.215 --> 01:08.416
It's a costume.

01:08.450 --> 01:10.186
She's the next Greta...

01:10.218 --> 01:11.354
something.

01:11.387 --> 01:13.189
Gosh! I wish I could remember
her last name.

01:13.221 --> 01:15.024
- She's so important.
- I bet.

01:15.057 --> 01:16.092
Will Cooper.

01:16.125 --> 01:18.194
Vice Principal Yarble! How are you?

01:18.226 --> 01:19.761
Terrible.

01:19.795 --> 01:22.665
I was taking a cat nap when your
daughter's screams awakened me.

01:22.697 --> 01:23.732
Make her stop.

01:23.765 --> 01:25.734
Let me coast into the sweet embrace

01:25.768 --> 01:27.236
of a three-day weekend.

01:27.268 --> 01:28.870
I already laid out my pajamas.

01:28.903 --> 01:30.211
Oh, she'll stop as soon as you agree

01:30.267 --> 01:31.602
to let us take Pete home
for the weekend.

01:31.656 --> 01:32.929
Oh, no.

01:32.969 --> 01:35.010
Then another kid will want
to take him home next weekend,

01:35.044 --> 01:36.411
and another,

01:36.444 --> 01:38.714
and soon I'll be running
some kind of check-out process.

01:38.747 --> 01:41.417
Don't make my life harder, Will Cooper.
Please, I can't take it.

01:41.450 --> 01:45.121
Well, then, I'm sorry to say,
Sophie's campaign will continue.

01:45.153 --> 01:47.056
No! No! Pete can't stay!

01:47.089 --> 01:48.123
That's my girl.

01:48.157 --> 01:51.226
Greta Thunberg! Ah, that's the name.
I remembered.

01:51.259 --> 01:52.727
Now, that is a face to silk-screen.

01:52.760 --> 01:53.962
Sophie!

01:53.995 --> 01:56.065
Release Rocco from the headlock.

01:56.098 --> 01:58.200
That's not how we want
to get our signatures.

01:58.232 --> 02:00.097
Rocco, sign the petition.

